		"body": "The current version of Joplin disables the \"Copy\" command from the edit menu when in view mode. While this may not be a major issue on other platforms, on macOS the Cmd+C shortcut relies on the presence of the \"Copy\" item in the menu. As a result, this behavior prevents users from using the Cmd+C shortcut to copy in view mode on macOS. This PR fixes the issue.",
